Feature: Publish merged report to Xray

    As Xray Connector,
    I want to publish the merged test execution report to Xray
    So that test execution results are available in Xray

    @xray
    Scenario: Publish execution report

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-48'
        And   The merged report directory is 'test/fixtures/reports/merged/RDCHAPQA-48'
        And   The report test environment is not set
        When  Xray Connector publishes test execution report to Xray
        Then  No execution error should be reported

    @xray
    Scenario: Publish execution report with gatling report url

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-45'
        And   The merged report directory is 'test/fixtures/reports/merged/RDCHAPQA-45'
        And   The report test environment is not set
        And   The gatling report url is 'https://gitlabee.dt.renault.com'
        When  Xray Connector publishes test execution report to Xray
        Then  No execution error should be reported

    @xray
    Scenario: Publish execution report with gatling test plan and labels

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-45'
        And   The merged report directory is 'test/fixtures/reports/merged/RDCHAPQA-45'
        And   The report test environment is not set
        And   The test plan file is 'test/fixtures/test-plan.json'
        And   The test labels are 'test-label-1,test-label-2'
        When  Xray Connector publishes test execution report to Xray
        Then  No execution error should be reported

    @xray
    Scenario: Publish execution report with environment information

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-48'
        And   The merged report directory is 'test/fixtures/reports/merged/RDCHAPQA-48'
        And   The report test environment is 'QUA'
        When  Xray Connector publishes test execution report to Xray
        Then  No execution error should be reported
